<l>naṉaviṉā ṉalkā tavaraik kaṉaviṉāṟ </l>
<l>kāṇṭali ṉuṇṭeṉ ṉuyir</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My life lasts because in my dream I behold him who does not favour me in my waking hours.</l>
